Name: Steven Fook Yuan Wong

About: Steven graduated from UC Davis on December 2006 with a B.A. in Film Studies and Economics.  He was formerly the president of Filmmakers Ambitions and an officer of Robotmedia Davis.  In addition, he was a member of the Asian American Association Film Festival Committee.  Before he graduated, he was involved in Matt Brewbakers 16mm zombie film http://www.lostinzombieville.com Lost in Zombieville as a producer, casting director, secondunit director, and promoter.
